title: #191 - Jeffree Star Goofs Up & Marc Rebillet Live
description:
On this episode of the H3 Podcast we are joined by the eminently talented musician Marc Rebillet!  We also discuss Jeffree Star's new cremated make-up line, Laurie Laughlin goin to the slammer, personal bubbles at Chik-fil-A, and a whole lot more!
 You can get tickets to Marc's upcoming drive-in tour at http://iwannahotbox.com
